程序包 org.springframework.boot.actuate.autoconfigure.endpoint

Core classes for actuator endpoint auto-configuration.

请参阅: 说明

  • 类概要 
    类 说明
    DefaultCachingConfigurationFactory
    Default CachingConfigurationFactory implementation that use the Environment to extract the caching settings of each endpoint.
    EndpointAutoConfiguration
    Auto-configuration for Endpoint support.
    EndpointEnablement
    Determines if an endpoint is enabled or not.
    EndpointEnablementProvider
    Determines an endpoint's enablement based on the current Environment.
    EndpointProvider<T extends Operation>
    Provides the endpoints that are enabled according to an EndpointDiscoverer and the current Environment.
